text_raw:
2. The 30th day of June 2025 is appointed as the day on which the Finance 
(Provision of Access to Cash Infrastructure) Act 2025 (No. 4 of 2025) shall come 
into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

11 June, 2025. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 13th June, 2025.
